{"tid":550214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連老一輩都知道政府係戇鳩","createTime":"2018-02-04T14:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T15:07:29.000Z","uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4094c5c01090a95b3c4b78f4913f1acd825db5b0","tid":550214,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:15:26.000Z","msg":"我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下對話內容：<br />\n<br />\n我：咁耐冇返香港，呢排香港點呀？<br />\n<br />\n老豆：林鄭上台之後呀，連啲公立醫生都帶人遊花園啦！<br />\n<br />\n我：咩意思？<br />\n<br />\n老豆：前幾日去公家睇症，諗住搞搞個痔瘡，又話我高血壓糖尿病，要進一步檢查，要我再輪候覆診。<br />\n<br />\n我：哇！咁大鑊？<br />\n<br />\n老豆：挑你都戇鳩，之後去x醫生度私人幫我做bodycheck，咩事都冇！爽手就幫我做咗痔瘡手術。以後都唔睇公家，都係睇翻x醫生可靠啲。<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (心諗原來香港醫療咁痴線)"},{"pid":"bdd8dd230f2458beb3f77185c25afcb216dd9b2d","tid":550214,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"又踩港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e073757b7b5f2004c83c6eb9002d4e906cc127","tid":550214,"uid":49392,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"世伯自己利益受損咪識咁講囉，其他老嘢有蛇齋餅粽就鬧後生反對政府搞搞震"},{"pid":"2f32c1a161d6184482e6316bb4809a79f499d310","tid":550214,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"啲手術做唔切，無人做<br />\n咪搵其他野攝你時間谷你去私院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e71c04dc6c1502e1f0e16601b328fb9b6f1ddc","tid":550214,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又踩港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n膠都廢事畀"},{"pid":"0446bb0ef41e57e78a60c6a483a7eb39bfa36748","tid":550214,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2